title: Brady Quinn on NFL Week 5 action, Drew Brees breaks passing record (Football 10/09)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner to break down the historic performance by Drew Brees against the Redskins in the Saints shellacking of Washington on Monday night. Then Brady Quinn joins Will to break down all the biggest storylines from the week that was in the NFL.
